      • execute

        public void execute(results.netlist.Netlist netlist,
                    TargetData targetData,
                    NetlistConstraint netlistConstraint,
                    AlgorithmProfile AProfile,
                    RuntimeEnv runtimeEnv)
        Executes the algorithm. Executes the following methods in sequential order:
        getConstraintFromNetlistConstraintFile()
        getDataFromUCF()
        setParameterValues()
        validateParameterValues()
        preprocessing()
        run()
        postprocessing()
        Parameters:
        netlist - Netlist used during execution
        targetData - TargetData used during execution
        netlistConstraint - NetlistConstraint used during execution
        AProfile - AlgorithmProfile used during execution
        runtimeEnv - RuntimeEnv used during execution
        Throws:
        java.lang.RuntimeException - if any of the parameters are null
